Package database

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Database
    Database.java has methods to set up a connection with the database and handle SQL queries.
    DataHandler
    This class consists of methods to verify if the user has entered the correct E-mail address, has followed the password rules and re-entered it correctly and includes a method to hash the password of the user before storing it to the database.
    FileManager
    File manager uses JSch in order to implement methods of uploading, downloading and deleting files from our server via sftp.
    House
    A class that will hold information for houses.
    HouseImage
    Holds images and associated information.
    HouseReview
    Holds information for a house review.
    HouseVideo
    Holds a video and associated data.
    Marker
    Holds information for a video marker.
    Search
    A class that contains methods used in searching for houses.
    SQLFilter
    This class restricts the users to enter SQL keywords into textfields, which might otherwise be executed into the database.
    User
    Holds information associated with a user.
    UserReview
    Holds user review information.
